Note: `position of <needle> in <haystack>` dispatches to string_find for String
Note: haystacks. Returns the byte index of the first match, or -1 if not found.
Note: Position of ":" in "key:value" is 3.
Note: Expected exit code: 3

Process called "main" returns Integer:
    Let s be "key:value"
    Let p be position of ":" in s
    Return p
End Process
